    "description_long": "This is a small, enclosed graveyard featuring a central stone mausoleum with a gabled roof and block-patterned walls. The mausoleum is flanked by two upright rectangular headstones, each set on a raised stone base. The entire graveyard is surrounded by a black wrought iron fence with stone pillars at the corners and a prominent front gate. The ground is covered in green grass, and the area within the fence is neatly maintained. The structure and materials suggest a traditional, urban cemetery plot, with the mausoleum serving as the focal point.",
